1
00:00:01,339 --> 00:00:02,340
Bruce Wayne?

2
00:00:03,020 --> 00:00:04,020
You peaked.

3
00:00:04,300 --> 00:00:06,780
I won't have vigilantism in my town.

4
00:00:07,140 --> 00:00:08,300
You'll be rid of me.

5
00:00:09,020 --> 00:00:10,760
As soon as I find the Joker.

6
00:00:11,200 --> 00:00:12,880
That may not be soon enough.

7
00:00:17,860 --> 00:00:19,820
It doesn't take much, does it?

8
00:00:20,220 --> 00:00:23,100
The Joker has 20 pounds more where this
came from.

9
00:00:23,800 --> 00:00:25,220
Thought you might like to know.

